videos.description: David Pindell evades the Rhode Island defense and runs in an early touchdown for UConn.
videos.headline: UConn's Pindell scrambles for 17-yard TD

videos.description: Rhode Island's Marven Beauvais gets pushed out of bounds but recovers to catch a 22-yard touchdown from JaJuan Lawson.
videos.headline: RI's Lawson finds Beauvais in the end zone for 22-yard TD

videos.description: Kevin Mensah finds a hole in the Rhode Island defense and takes it in for a UConn touchdown.
videos.headline: UConn RB Mensah rushes for 11-yard TD

videos.description: UConn's Oneil Robinson dives to pick off Rhode Island QB JaJuan Lawson.
videos.headline: UConn's Robinson lays out for INT

videos.description: David Pindell finds Heron Maurisseau and he leaves Rhode Island defenders in the dust for a 74-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UConn's Maurisseau left wide open for long TD

videos.description: JaJuan Lawson loses the ball at the goal line, but the 37-yard touchdown run for Rhode Island is confirmed after further review.
videos.headline: Rhode Island QB nearly fumbles at goal line on TD run

videos.description: David Pindell throws a back-shoulder fade to Hergy Mayala for a 13-yard score.
videos.headline: UConn's Mayala catches 2nd TD from Pindell

videos.description: UConn QB David Pindell darts a 19-yard score to Aaron McLean, giving him four passing and a rushing touchdown in the first half vs. Rhode Island.
videos.headline: Pindell's pass gives him 5 total TDs in first half

videos.description: UConn QB David Pindell rushes in his second score of the game, to go along with his four passing touchdowns.
videos.headline: UConn's Pindell runs in for his 6th total TD on the day

videos.description: Naim Jones refuses to be tackled and forces his way in for a 14-yard touchdown to even the score at 49.
videos.headline: Rhode Island RB Jones scores, ties UConn at 49
